Manufacturer's Brand Overview
Hawaiian OLA is a Healthy Energy Shot made from Hawaiian Noni and other super fruits. OLA is made organically and sources fair trade ingredients to stay mindful of the people that grow our fruit and the planet that makes it possible. OLA contains 140mg of caffeine from organic Mate and Green Tea extracts to give bodies lasting energy without any harmful chemicals, dyes, or preservatives. Edit/Update


 877-729-2717
        







