Kona Coffee Leaf Tea Unflavored Loose Leaf









Kona Coffee Leaf Tea Unflavored Loose Leaf
32.99
Lightly-caffeinated Arabica Coffee leaves harvested from the Kona coast of Hawai'i Island.Good For YouCoffee leaf tea is a more potent source of antioxidants than green tea or traditionally brewed coffee. Coffee leaf is also rich in Mangiferin, which is being studied for its many potential health benefits.Good For HawaiiCoffee leaf is sustainably harvested during the regular pruning of mature coffee trees. The added value to farmers supports their labor intensive efforts to produce coffee responsibly in Hawaii.BrewingAdd 2.5g (two teaspoons) to 8ounces of hot water & steep to taste.Ingredients: 100% Organic Kona Coffee Leaves


